<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><SUB><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">\'Plato\'
in his famous book \'The Republic\' gives us an example of a sweet shop
owner and a doctor being contestants for an election. The sweetshop
owner while giving his election debate brags about how he will make
all the sweets free to eat and no restriction on anybody to eat as
much. Then Plato asks, what should the Doctor say? If he says I do
what I do for the benefit of the people, I open skulls, cause you
trouble, just to make you better- wouldn\'t sound great for an
election speech, right? And ultimately the sweet seller wins. This is
what is happening in our modern day politics as well. We want more
doctors and not sweet sellers to actually benefit the society. But
for that, two things need to happen, the doctors should come forward
and the public needs to be educated in a way they understand. HKUST
will give me the skills to become a doctor, a public policy
enthusiast already, I need to hone my skills and sharpen my prowess
to command a great change in our education system. Secondly, I have
already embarked on the vision of \'educating all\' and I tend to do
this in an innovative way of taking traditional knowledge
dissemination as premise and novel technology as the pedagogy. My
mission is to teach the voters of tomorrow, to participate in
democracy as informed individuals, not lured by some sweet seller and
that is how I think the real change shall come. The MPP program at
HKUST will be the batteries in the torch of this bearer, me. I
believe, that the foundation shall guide the way both for me to
realise my mission and for others to be part of it.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SUB></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">I
dedicated my Undergrad years to give voices to the deaf and mute.
With my small group\'s combined efforts, we made the training of
\'Indian sign language\' mandatory for the </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">Delhi</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">
Police taking the premise of rising rape cases against the women of
the community and their inability to report them. I further went on
to establish the first community souvenir store which helped deaf and
mute women gain employment by creating beautiful handicrafts as
souvenirs for the University. This small store led to the development
of one of the biggest online store selling products made by only
grassroots organisations as </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">Lithics.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">in.
I am a proud founder of that initiative which has registered more
than 10,000 direct beneficiaries as of now. </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">I
have been the beneficiary of the prestigious </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">DO
School</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">
