the </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">Up
Network</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">
where 197 youth of the region were enrolled under apprenticeship
program to gain sustainable employment. We established a small
manufacturing unit of bamboo products, giving employment
opportunities to 27 youngsters and it continues to grow.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=JUSTIFY STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
