<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#212529"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><SUB><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=4 STYLE="font-size: 16pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Essay
Question 1: Identify an issue in your community that concerns you.
How would you like to address this issue?</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SUB></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<OL>
<LI><P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">One
issue that I have been working on since past one year is to ensure
quality education and bring down the drop-out rates of community
schools in at-risk areas of India.As India nears universal
enrolment, there is a growing realization that bringing children
into schools doesn’t equate to quality learning. In fact, as the
conversation has moved away from enrolment, there is an active shift
towards seeking factors that deliver and influence quality. There
are more than 400,000 community schools in India. But numerous
problems like poor school infrastructure and learning environment,
lack of adequately trained teachers, high teacher absenteeism, a
large volume of teacher vacancies, low levels of learning and
achievement and lack of accountability to name a few contribute to a
staggering dropout rate that sees nearly 50% of children abandoning
their education at the key transitional ages of school. Well, for me
to start with, tackling all of these problems together would be
equivalent to trying to push a wall. Hence, my motivation is towards
solving one, ‘the quality of content delivery and
facilitation’.Knowledge nowadays is merely theoretical, taught
like a formality, with no applications. The purpose of knowledge
accumulated throughout thousands of years, we have forgotten. The
method of imparting knowledge has not changed, despite the vast
syllabi, our system continues to hold onto the orthodox methodology.
Some children, if not all, do not find anything enthusiastic, yet
they continue to churn the words to make sense and fail miserably.
To give a sustainable solution, I founded an organisation i.e.
‘</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">Maslow</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">
Initiative Foundation’ which works with community schools across
India. And we call the project ‘Abrazos’ which means embracing.
As the name goes, we literally adopt and embrace these schools and
implement our innovative learning methodology.Now for the
implementation part, I have started working with the ‘community
schools’ first because it is the only entity with no set
curriculum or teachers per se. There are more than 400,000 \'major\'
community schools in India and almost one in each village/town. We
are adopting such schools one by one and delivering our content to
change lives and improve student retention rates which happen to be
less than 10%.  In the 10+ schools that we have already adopted, we
showcase this digital content using projectors. The content is
prepared in the guidance of experts who help us develop
context-based graphical and story oriented content in more than 12
regional languages. This special pedagogy targets the traditional
methods of knowledge dissemination where pictures and folklore are
used to both transfer knowledge and develop interest among
4-16-year-olds. The program in each village is supported by the mere
contribution of just INR1 by each resident which in turn ensures
quality education in the most remote regions of the country. As of
today, we have over 2000 children being supported by this program
which tells us that this is a scalable solution and I need support
and guidance to make it work nationwide.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
</OL>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><B><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">2.
Essay Question 2: Describe one time you have been faced with a
challenge and had to use a leadership skill to come up with a
solution.</SPAN></B></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">
</SPAN></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">It
was the time when I was working with the Government of India\'s
project named \'Clean India Movement\' or the Swachh Bharat Abhiyan as
it is popularly known as. Under the scheme, I was heading the team
which was designated with the responsibility of motivating people to
construct toilets/latrines in their homes. India has long faced this
criticism and it has quite a lot maligned the country\'s image when it
comes to hygiene. The people are not willing to construct a toilet
inside the premises of their homes because of various cultural and
religious issues with absolutely no solid premise. Because of this,
over 40% of the rape cases that happen in rural areas are because of
the reason that women go out alone in the dark for the natural call. </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">So,
when we were out in the field and I was given the charge of two of
the most adamant cities, Hapur and Ghaziabad which have a long
history of not complying with authorities.  </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">When
our team approached the individual houses, we were greeted with
straight faces and threats to life. I knew that putting force and
making the reluctant people do something by subjugation wouldn\'t
solve the problem, so I introduced a moral tactic. With the help of
local authorities, I identified a woman in each village who had
undergone molestation or rape (due to not having toilets in homes)
and was courageous enough to lodge a public complaint. I made them
the leaders of the individual teams and let them lead the small units
to approach the other women in other houses. I knew that a woman to
woman talk would be much more effective and that too when coming from
a victim of such an event the primary cause of which was the absence
of toilets in homes. Also, it was the woman in the house who had the
highest capability to persuade the men of the house to make the
construction of the toilet possible. We made sure that each household
that agreed to construct one got a handsome compensation to do so
from the government. Not to our surprise, we registered 4400 requests
for toilet construction within 4 months of hard work. I don\'t just
consider it my individual achievement, but the achievement of the
entire unit working with us who actually realised my idea and backed
my leadership.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#212529"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=4 STYLE="font-size: 16pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Please
describe any experiences you may have had in community or grassroots
work.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#212529"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">I
dedicated my Undergrad years to give voices to the deaf and mute.
With my small group\'s combined efforts, we made the training of
\'Indian sign language\' mandatory for the </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#212529"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">Delhi</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#212529"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">
Police taking the premise of rising rape cases against the women of
the community and their inability to report them. I further went on
to establish the first community souvenir store which helped deaf and
mute women gain employment by creating beautiful handicrafts as
souvenirs for the University. This small store led to the development
of one of the biggest online store selling products made by only
grassroots organisations as </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#212529"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">Lithics.in</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#212529"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">.
I am a proud founder of that initiative which has registered more
than 10,000 direct beneficiaries as of now. </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#212529"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">I
have been the beneficiary of the prestigious </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#212529"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">DO
School</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#212529"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">
Fellowship, Germany during the time of which I worked in the
underdeveloped area of Duque de Caxias in Rio, Brazil under the
Entrepreneurship for Good Program and started an initiative called
the </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#212529"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">Up
Network</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#212529"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">
where 197 youth of the region were enrolled under apprenticeship
program to gain sustainable employment. We established a small
manufacturing unit of bamboo products, giving employment
opportunities to 27 youngsters and it continues to grow.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
