<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#666666"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><SUB><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 13pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><B><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">What
concrete impact is your current work having? What are the values that
motivate you? Please include any challenges you have faced in this
work, and how you have sought to overcome them. (300 words or fewer)
*</SPAN></B></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SUB></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#666666"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">After
three years of extensive experience in the social-startup scene,
travelling to 30 countries, working in 13 states of India, learning
three languages, receiving four international fellowships,
successfully celebrating first anniversary of my long-distance
relationship and starting and taking India\'s first online marketplace
for and by the underserved (</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#666666"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">Lithics.in</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#666666"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">)
to clocking five digit direct beneficiary numbers, I finally founded
a non-profit organisation i.e. ‘</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#666666"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">Maslow
</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#666666"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Initiative
Foundation’. MIF works with community schools across India. And we
call the project ‘Abrazos’ which means embracing. As the name
goes, we literally adopt and embrace these schools and implement our
innovative learning methodology to make sure that the most basic
human right, the Right to Education is properly addressed. I believe
and I am, a strong advocate of value-based experiential learning
rather than theoretical bookish knowledge dissemination. India, the
land of ‘vedas’, proudly owning millions of books and artefacts
which deliver knowledge in a purposeful and practical way are being
subtly lost. </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#666666"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">But
we have started the revival. The lessons, be it of science,
mathematics or humanities, are all taught using storytelling and
pictures using digital methods developed by our organisation. The use
of a simple projector and a USB with numerous resources of digital
learning and simple technology in the community schools of India at
the most remote places.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#666666"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Working
in the remotest parts of the country is a tough job and the
traditionalists a tough nut to crack but still we have managed to
deliver 800 digital books across these villages in more than 30
community schools with 6000+ direct beneficiaries. We have partnered
with local NGOs and are developing one of India\'s biggest community
network of volunteers who are vocationally trained by my other
initiative, upnetwork.org. These volunteers are helping us spread the
reality of our vision in an exponential way.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#666666"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 13pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><B><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Why
do you want to be an Obama Foundation Scholar? (300 words or fewer)&nbsp;</SPAN></B></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#666666"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">\'Plato\'
in his famous book \'The Republic\' gives us an example of a sweet shop
owner and a doctor being contestants for an election. The sweetshop
owner while giving his election debate brags about how he will make
all the sweets free to eat and no restriction on anybody to eat as
much. Then Plato asks, what should the Doctor say? If he says I do
what I do for the benefit of the people, I open skulls, cause you
trouble, just to make you better- wouldn\'t sound great for an
election speech, right? And ultimately the sweet seller wins. This is
what is happening in our modern day politics as well. We want more
doctors and not sweet sellers to actually benefit the society. But
for that, two things need to happen, the doctors should come forward
and the public needs to be educated in a way they understand. Obama
Foundation will give me the skills to become a doctor, a public
policy enthusiast already, I need to hone my skills and sharpen my
prowess to command a great change in our education system. Secondly,
I have already embarked on the vision of \'educating all\' and I tend
to do this in an innovative way of taking traditional knowledge
dissemination as premise and novel technology as the pedagogy. My
mission is to teach the voters of tomorrow, to participate in
democracy as informed individuals, not lured by some sweet seller and
that is how I think the real change shall come. Obama Foundation and
Columbia University will be the batteries in the torch of this
bearer, me. I believe, that the foundation shall guide the way both
for me to realise my mission and for others to be part of it.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#666666"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 13pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><B><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Describe
a problem within your community, country, or region that you would
like to address when you return after finishing the Obama Foundation
Scholars Program. What are the obstacles to addressing this problem,
and how would you seek to overcome them? (300 words or fewer) *</SPAN></B></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 115%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arial, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">As
India nears universal enrolment, there is a growing realization that
bringing children into schools doesn’t equate to quality learning.
In fact, as the conversation has moved away from enrolment, there is
an active shift towards seeking factors that deliver and influence
access and quality. There are more than 1 million public schools in
India. But numerous problems like poor school infrastructure and
learning environment, lack of adequately trained teachers, high
teacher absenteeism, no internet or technology use, and lack of
accessibility to name a few, contribute to a staggering dropout rate
that sees nearly 50% of children abandoning their education at the
key transitional ages of school. Well, for me to start with, tackling
all of these problems together would be equivalent to trying to push
a wall. Hence, my motivation is towards solving one, ‘quality of
content delivery and ensuring accessibility’. </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 115%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 115%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arial, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">It
is the proliferation of experiential context-based learning (which we
are making completely digital) that is missing. And poor students
have no idea about what they are being deprived of. If not for the
\'community schools\', the children will be forced into hazardous job
sectors such as firecracker industries, rag-picking and prostitution.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 115%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 115%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arial, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Now
for the implementation part, I have started working with the
‘community schools’ first because it is the only entity with no
set curriculum or teachers per-se and most of them are situated in
remote at-risk areas. There are more than 400,000 major community
schools in India and almost one in each village/town. We are adopting
such schools one by one and delivering our content, which requires
absolutely no teacher facilitation and is made interesting enough
using graphics and animations in 12 regional languages and seven
different subjects (which our partners and mentors are curating), to
change lives and improve student retention rates.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 115%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 115%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 115%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arial, serif"><FONT SIZE=3><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><B><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Any
other information.</SPAN></B></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; line-height: 115%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 115%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arial, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">The
content development specifically is being supported by </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arial, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">UNESCO</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arial, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">
APCEIU, South Korea from where I received a fellowship in the domain
of Global Citizenship Education, which also happens to be one of our
subjects offered. The content delivery and accessibility is being
ensured and supported by the Internet Society itself as I am an
Internet Society Fellow as well. The we have the </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arial, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">DO
School</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arial, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">,
Germany and </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arial, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">Sinal
do Vale</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arial, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">,
Brazil as our mentors and patrons who are working for the 
