of the world. Which is why YGS is a necessary platform for the exchange of ideas and bring the world </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_103:150" style="top:150;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
together simultaneously to have open discussions about the social issues most prominent to our world </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_103:168" style="top:168;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
today. The world leaders may already be propagating the broader realities but they are more often than </span>
