<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
not veiled by the electoral and nationalistic interests which may side-blind them necessarily. This is why </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_103:203" style="top:203;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
a forum like YGS which is a youth convergence platform fills that void and brings the youth to the </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_103:220" style="top:220;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
mainstream decision making process where they have a chance to influence the masses by proliferating </span>
