<div class="pos" id="_103:238" style="top:238;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
their ideas and work whilst keeping China as a polar star to navigate their own countries\' ways and needs </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_103:256" style="top:256;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
and discover newer paths for regions also other than theirs.</span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:273" style="top:273;left:78">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
2. Being an Indian, the image of China was always put as a competitor and a dominant neighbour. While </span>
