<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
neighbour. My China story has a lot do with the way people are indulged in national interests and work </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_103:379" style="top:379;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
towards one goal- putting their country on the top of everyone else. This zeal I have seen at every place </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_103:396" style="top:396;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
that I have been in China so far.  I am both surprised and motivated by how the Chinese mentality of co-</span>
