<div class="pos" id="_103:431" style="top:431;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
feeling back to my home country and would like to replicate the Chinese methodology to enhance the </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_103:449" style="top:449;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
driving force behind the many facets of daily life which impact a nation\'s collective growth.</span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:466" style="top:466;left:78">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
3. To me the theme delves into the narrative of China created by the world at large. China, being a closed </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_103:484" style="top:484;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
nation for long, has not sought many global citizens historically. The Chinese are being inquisitive now </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_103:502" style="top:502;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
and so is the rest of the world. What factors behold China\'s growth and continued success, and how did it </span>
