<div class="pos" id="_103:783" style="top:783;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
Doesn\'t it look like something that should be changed? We need people to come out and explore the </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_103:800" style="top:800;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
revered or the feared. To break stereotypes, to venture out and learn from practical experiences. Hence </span>
