<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
a sense of trust between two nations.</span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:870" style="top:870;left:78">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
5. Meeting and interacting with such people who share a common humanity and believe in themselves as </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_103:888" style="top:888;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
global citizens are the best fellow audience one can get to proliferate the workable ideas for the benefit </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_103:906" style="top:906;left:103">
<span id="_14.8" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14.8px; color:#000000">
of the entire \'overlooked community&#146; and the countrymen under the veil of ignorance. I believe that the </span>
