</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 9pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">I
have by far worked with many communities including but not limited to
refugees, deaf and mute community, street kids, rural artisans and
out of school children. My passion is not just defined by the work
that I have done while working with them but also, the post-
completion of my initiatives which have prompted even my country’s
national government to implement the policy measures which were
suggested out of my interventions. </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 9pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">My
social enterprise has registered over 10,000 direct beneficiaries and
over 40,000 indirect ones in just over one year of operation. We have
not just provided our beneficiaries with the financial support crutch
but also empowered them to become self-sustaining individuals by
ensuring employment for 400 men and women who gained permanent
positions in our partner grassroots organisations and are leading an
honourable life today.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 9pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">One
issue that I have been working on since past one year is to ensure
quality education and bring down the drop-out rates of community
schools in at-risk areas of India.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 9pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">As
India nears universal enrolment, there is a growing realization that
bringing children into schools doesn’t equate to quality learning.
In fact, as the conversation has moved away from enrolment, there is
an active shift towards seeking factors that deliver and influence
quality. There are more than 400,000 community schools in India. But
numerous problems like poor school infrastructure and learning
environment, lack of adequately trained teachers, high teacher
absenteeism, a large volume of teacher vacancies, low levels of
learning and achievement and lack of accountability to name a few
contribute to a staggering dropout rate that sees nearly 50% of
children abandoning their education at the key transitional ages of
school. Well, for me to start with, tackling all of these problems
together would be equivalent to trying to push a wall. Hence, my
motivation is towards solving one, ‘the quality of content delivery
and facilitation’.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 9pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">To
give a sustainable solution, I founded an organisation i.e. ‘</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 9pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">Maslow</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 9pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">
Initiative Foundation’ which works with community schools across
India. And we call the project ‘Abrazos’ which means embracing.
As the name goes, we literally adopt and embrace these schools and
implement our innovative learning methodology.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 9pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Now
for the implementation part, I have started working with the
‘community schools’ first because it is the only entity with no
set curriculum or teachers per say. There are more than 400,000 major
community schools in India,  and almost one in each village/town. We
are adopting such schools one by one and delivering our content to
change lives and improve student retention rates which happens to be
less than 10%. </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 9pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">In
the 10+ schools that we have already adopted, we showcase this
digital content using projectors. Projector as a medium because,
first, they are cheaper than computers or tablets (&lt;USD 12);
second, can cater to a larger audience at once. Then comes the
content transportation, which we do using flash drives, which is the
cheapest method to do so. As of today, we have over 2000 children
being supported by this program and that is what quenches my thirst
to bring change and make a difference.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=2 STYLE="font-size: 9pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Being
raised in a family where the struggle was real, I have seen the
problems that I am working on first hand and hence have developed
that inherent passion to change what I was just forced to accept in
my childhood. I see the world with the perspective of providing
solutions and like to call myself as a social enthusiast who is out
there amending the dented. </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">
</SPAN></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><BR>
</P>
<DIV TYPE=FOOTER>
<P CLASS="western" STYLE="margin-top: 0.16in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; text-decoration: none">
<BR>
</P>
</DIV>
