</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">In
the year 2017, when I was undergoing my bachelors’ program in
Islamabad, Pakistan, I got an opportunity to work with WWF (World
Wildlife Fund). </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Islamabad
is famous for its high peaks and beautiful mountain range known as
Margalla Hills and this hill has 6 trails of different lengths for
public use. WWF formed small teams comprising 3 members each and our
task was to run awareness campaign about, growing littering problems
on these trails and major cause were those public convenience stalls
being run alongside the road. As when people buy food and water there
were no proper places for recycling and they were forced to throw
them on trails.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">There
were 30 stalls that I was responsible to handle in terms of awareness
campaign. I was able to persuade them to install Recycle bins and
enlighten them about three bin system and not just provided them but
they actually paid for those bins. After working for several days, I
was able to secure 27 stalls to place 3 bin system next to their
stall. </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Now,
whenever I go to those trails I feel gratified that people really
have stopped littering and since the tourism and local footfall has
increased significantly, Government has also taken this issue in to
account and now it is mandatory for everyone to have bins next to
their food stalls.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
