<DIV TYPE=HEADER>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.46in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
</DIV>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#2d1530"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><SUB><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><B><SPAN STYLE="background: #f7f5f5">Provide
an example of something you have done, built or created that shows
your exceptional ability or skill (something that most of your peers
could not, or would not have done)</SPAN></B></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SUB></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#db2a3a"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #f7f5f5">&nbsp;*</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#2d1530"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arimo, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff"><BR></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#2d1530"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><I><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #f7f5f5">Examples
include technology, work, side projects, clubs or societies have you
created, built or made an exceptional contribution to. &nbsp;Feel
free to include awards, scholarships or prizes you have won. Provide
URLs where relevant and numbers to show your level of contribution.</SPAN></SPAN></I></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<IMG SRC="568bbd8ded5722a0b12039b8864e7ea9_html_2b843a41.png" NAME="image1.png" ALIGN=BOTTOM HSPACE=12 WIDTH=243 HEIGHT=89 BORDER=0></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">It
was the year 2016 when  I started my business Triangles (Fast Food
Restaurant) which was formed on the grounds of not wasting food and
empowering low wage income people in nearby area while earning
profits at the same time.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">First
few months went by and restaurant was doing well as in the beginning
word of mouth and friends and family were good enough to boost sales
by hosting events and large gatherings. After 7 months we started to
face competition in terms of marketing since market was getting
denser day by day and our market share started to decrease.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">We
had to come up with a marketing plan, back then, marketing was mainly
done by flyer distribution at door steps considering there were more
than 10,000 houses in our target area in which there were more than
57000 people living (According to local society office). Our main
target was to do flyer distribution once a week to all these 10000
houses for better brand recall and recognition. At that time people
were not generally into digital media for ordering food and whole
industry was working on physical advertisements.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">One
finest option (which all competitors were using) was to hire some
freelancers which were charging rs.2 per flyer and they were able to
cover 700-800 houses per day and even that according to their time
schedule (i.e. if we want to do some weekend per month end promotion
we can never be sure that our flyer will reach our audience at the
right time). At that time, market was competing in a way that whoever
wins this part of flyer distribution- will actually have the biggest
advantage as this was the only possible and feasible mode of doing
marketing at the time. One flyer was costing us 3 rupees and
distribution cost was rupees 2 adding up to total 5 rupees with no
guarantee of our flyer reaching our customer (because no way to track
if freelancers are actually delivering flyers or just throwing all of
them to waste) and on top of that producing analytics was difficult
since everything was done manually and there was no record.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Being
Co-founder and person handling operations and marketing all the
burden was on my shoulder in making such a strategy that could work
for us and can help us in getting competitive advantage. So, there
were 2 main issues</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<UL>
<LI><P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Cost
was high.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<LI><P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Inability
to trust distributors because of no check and balance.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<LI><P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Tracking
and analytics were impossible for the marketing activities taken up
were next to impossible</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
</UL>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Solving
this seemingly  difficult but very practical issue gave me chills as
a founder. I delved into finding a solution and finally settled for
good to create an app using the resources from one of my other
ventures which happens to be a Software House or a tech incubation
space where we take up outsourced projects in the field of
technology. And as one would assume, the entire team readily agreed.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">App
was basically a GPS tracker that tracks your location as you move and
records very slight movements to go right and left and on elevation
(when actually moving towards and when stepping on ramp of a house).
It was also recording time and compiling all the data at the end of
month for analytics and studies (since there were more than one
distributor using it).</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">For
this work, by sticking to my business’s core value, we empowered
local labors who were working for rupees 400 per day for 8 hours. We
hired few of them and offered them rupees 600 per day and to work for
only 4 hours per day and they still can-do other job if they feel
like to, which brings down our cost of distribution to rupees 750
flyers(average) / 600rupees = 1.25rupees per flyer. So, we started to
save rupees 30,000 on our monthly marketing expenses.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">App
helped us track their movements and genuineness of their distribution
(they have to keep the app running from the phone provided by us, in
order to claim their commission at the end of day) and on top of that
it helped us reduce the cost of flyer distributed by 37.5%. Lastly,
we were able to have well managed analytics to analyze at the end of
period and improvise it with time.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Despite
all the team members against my idea in the beginning we managed to
make it work and it helped us in our cost cutting in many following
months.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR><BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#2d1530"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><B><SPAN STYLE="background: #f7f5f5">Provide
another example of something you have done, built or created that
shows your exceptional ability or skill</SPAN></B></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#db2a3a"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #f7f5f5">&nbsp;*</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#2d1530"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arimo, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff"><BR></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#2d1530"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><I><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #f7f5f5">Feel
free to either expand on your previous example, or to use a new
