<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Above
mentioned example didn’t end there</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">We
were successful in cost leadership but now, it was time to introduce
differentiation in to our business model. We knew that our idea was
working exceptionally well and we had put so much time and effort to
generate that idea and form the labors team and empowered them with
basic knowledge and to be honest it was too much effort being done to
save rs30,000. Undoubtedly it was more than good in the beginning and
surely helped us make competitive advantage but now after few months
it was time to come up with new strategies that can help us sustain
our restaurant marketing model. I always dreamed that maybe there is
a way that we can do all our marketing for free (because the day we
do marketing in general, we used to deliver double the number of
orders that day and that ended up being most satisfying moments for
me). Basically, I was addicted to it as to kind of happiness and
satisfaction I was getting out of it</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">One
day idea clicked in to mind and I discussed with my partner and team
mates. The idea was basically to outsource the distribution app and
help other businesses in terms of flyer distribution and earn some
revenues. There were a few questions</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<UL>
<LI><P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Why
would other businesses trust us?</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<LI><P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">How
would we differentiate ourselves from those freelancers?</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<LI><P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">What
cost benefits we can offer them?</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
</UL>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">To
answer all these questions, I again came up with a solution and this
time focus was to generate revenue and have some differentiation
advantages when being compared with competitors.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">In
order to answer these questions, I came up with proposal to other
businesses and we ask them to let us do your flyer distribution and
we offered them following perks</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<UL>
<LI><P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Only
0.75rs per flyer (with the option to redesign your flyer on
additional cost – Software house graphic designer started to get
additional customers).</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<LI><P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">App
analytics and proof of your flyers being distributed.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<LI><P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">3
cycles (time period) to choose from every week.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
</UL>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">We
managed to accomplish this as we printed envelope with our brandings
(Free advertisement for us) which costed us rs1.5 and inside we were
putting 5 flyers of different businesses (not necessarily on kind of
business) which helped us generate 3.75rs per envelope distributed.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">What
we were able to dig out of this was to market our brand thrice a week
as compared to once a week and now we are generating rs1 instead of
spending rs3.25. doing flyer distribution 3 times a week end up us
getting rs3 every week per envelope and distribution cost was same of
rs1.25 </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Now
we were generating in best times (when we were completing 3 rounds of
10000 houses every week having 5 pamphlets in one envelope) rs120,000
every month and plus we were saving expense to advertise our own
business by rs130,000.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#2d1530"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><B><SPAN STYLE="background: #f7f5f5">Provide
an (optional) extra example of something you have done, built or
created that shows your exceptional ability or skill</SPAN></B></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#2d1530"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Arimo, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff"><BR></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#2d1530"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><I><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #f7f5f5">If
you have another example you would like to share, please add it here</SPAN></SPAN></I></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; text-decoration: none; page-break-after: auto">
<BR><BR>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">I
have grown up in a society where parents’ dream is to see you
successful in terms of your education and no doubt in my country you
are being judged by how good of a college and university you have
studied from and you’ll be presented all the opportunities on these
grounds. So, struggle starts from early childhood when you are
supposed to study hard and learn as much as you can so that you can
get admission into good schools and colleges and then universities
then land a good job (it never ends basically) I was part of the same
herd and I did good, I’ve faced tough times i.e. when your national
tongue is Urdu, parents language is Punjabi and you are also supposed
to learn Arabic and medium of instruction in educational institutes
in English so our struggles starts form the very beginning when we
are born. </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>
</P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0.11in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 107%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">I
completed by school and college from the best institutes from my
country followed by my university which is one of the top for my
major (business administration). This race of being competitive
didn’t end there and now Master’s from one of the top institutes
was the priority and started to prepare myself for that.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-top: 0.06in; margin-bottom: 0.06in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#1d2129"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Virtually
nothing is impossible in this world if you just put your mind to it
and maintain a positive attitude.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-top: 0.06in; margin-bottom: 0.06in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#1d2129"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">It
was a time back in January after my graduation, when my knowledge was
nothing, but my aim was big, to get into at least into top 50 ranked
universities worldwide.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-top: 0.06in; margin-bottom: 0.06in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#1d2129"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">I
was really interested to go to </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#1d2129"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">China</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#1d2129"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">
from very early days of my planning and goal setting as because of
reasons much obvious, economic stability and future growth
predictions needs no introduction especially with respect to
Pakistan.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-top: 0.06in; margin-bottom: 0.06in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#1d2129"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">Surely,
It\'s a rough road but it\'s totally worth it</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-top: 0.06in; margin-bottom: 0.06in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
<SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#1d2129"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">First,
it looked very hard but I slowly I got used to it, communicating with
different people, finding useful tips and surfing through internet
all day long became my everyday routine and very habitual to me.</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P CLASS="western" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-top: 0.06in; margin-bottom: 0.06in; background: #ffffff; border: none; padding: 0in; line-height: 100%; page-break-inside: auto; widows: 2; orphans: 2; page-break-after: auto">
