The aim of a social enterprise is to benefit society and generate
profits simultaneously.  It is an ongoing process which
kaleidoscopically changes as to how the future of mankind looks.
Well, this thought led to the creation of </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#595d64"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=4><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">Lithics.in</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#595d64"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=4><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">.
</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#595d64"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=4><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #000000">Www.lithics.in</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-variant: normal"><FONT COLOR="#595d64"><SPAN STYLE="text-decoration: none"><FONT FACE="Helvetica Neue, serif"><FONT SIZE=4><SPAN STYLE="font-style: normal"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal"><SPAN STYLE="background: #ffffff">
is an online marketplace with products which contribute to a social
or environmental cause. We focus on market access, economic
empowerment, higher education and capacity building of NGOs, social
and environmental organisations, women, artisans, persons with
disability, jail inmates, migrants, refugees and tribal communities,
connect them to customers globally and help them create- secure and
sustainable livelihoods for themselves. “I believe that people can
overcome disadvantage and marginalization if they are empowered to be
better organised, resourced, supported, and can secure access to
