<div class="pos" id="_78:81" style="top:81;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style="font-weight:bold; font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
Part 2: Supplementary Information</span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:119" style="top:119;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
All of my studies have taken place in English language right from the elementary school up to my </span>
