<div class="pos" id="_78:138" style="top:138;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
bachelors. And additionally, I am a published English language novelist and poet as well. I wrote </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:157" style="top:157;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
my first novel fiction when I was 16 named \'Behind the Scenes\' and it eventually became a </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:176" style="top:176;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
bestseller. My poems have been published by the \'Ibiskos Risolo\' publishing house in Italy and the </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:195" style="top:195;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
