</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:234" style="top:234;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
Assimilation is always a hard path. Transitions are never easy to get past. Cultural differences are </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:253" style="top:253;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
bone chilling. And comfort is long lost. Seemed like the moon didn\'t shine anymore because it was </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:272" style="top:272;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
resonating its dullness with mine. Fellows were just running after grades and nobody was bothered </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:291" style="top:291;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
that Delhi had a student accommodation problem! Such was the state of my college life when I first </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:310" style="top:310;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
entered University as an undergrad. But fortunately enough, I wasn\'t among the ones ready to open </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:329" style="top:329;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
my mouth to spoon-fed knowledge just pushed down one\'s throat. I was there to affect the bigger </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:349" style="top:349;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
picture. </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:368" style="top:368;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
Looking around, I saw people who had been made part of the herd but still had that spark of </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:387" style="top:387;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
reluctance left which made them turn their heads in search of a similar vibe. I poached them from </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:406" style="top:406;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
the herd giving them a new life. With no money or networks, we started to build some. I started the </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:425" style="top:425;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
most successful film club, Delhi University has thus far seen and started screening movies which </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:444" style="top:444;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
may make people go for the greater good and break out of stereotypes and prejudices that hold them </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:464" style="top:464;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
back. I screened more than 70+ films from across the world and each film made possible over a </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:483" style="top:483;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
hundred students, professors, scholars, teachers to interact on issues which were never touched upon </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:502" style="top:502;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
in class because of \'one book one rule system\'! That got me started, I saw the power in making </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:521" style="top:521;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
connections and healthy collaborations. Being moderating more than 60 of those sessions I thought </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:540" style="top:540;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
that the entire city should become a part of it, well, still not sure how to achieve it, the best way I </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:559" style="top:559;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
thought was community radio. I established the first formal operational community radio program </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:579" style="top:579;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
at the University of Delhi and started creating sponsored programs on it- thus making my first </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:598" style="top:598;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
money, it was an exhilarating experience.</span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:617" style="top:617;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
I dedicated my second year at University to give voices to the deaf and mute. With my small </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:636" style="top:636;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
group\'s combined efforts, we made the training of \'Indian sign language\' mandatory for the Delhi </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:655" style="top:655;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
Police taking the premise of rising rape cases against the women of the community and their </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:674" style="top:674;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
inability to report them. I further went on to establish the first community souvenir store which </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:694" style="top:694;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
helped deaf and mute women gain employment by creating beautiful handicrafts as souvenirs for </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:713" style="top:713;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
the University. This small store led to the development of one of the biggest online store selling </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:732" style="top:732;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
products made by only grassroots organisations as Lithics.in. I am a proud founder of that initiative. </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:751" style="top:751;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
Having been involved with many underserved communities and watching them barely making it to </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:770" style="top:770;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
the next day, I decided to start my own non-profit, The Maslow Initiative Foundation which has </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:789" style="top:789;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
now touched four digit of direct beneficiaries and all of them being school going children. Now as </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:809" style="top:809;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
the organisation grows, I ought to be a better manager of everything and my vision and hence this </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:828" style="top:828;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
scholarship. I carry many more\'s dreams now and I want them to have the best of me and Asian </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:847" style="top:847;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
Future Leaders Scholarship Program assures that.</span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1000" style="top:1000;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style="font-weight:bold; font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
Part 3: Personal Statement</span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1039" style="top:1039;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
I have by far worked with many communities including but not limited to refugees, deaf and mute </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1058" style="top:1058;left:78">
<span id="_16.2" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.2px; color:#000000">
community, street kids, rural artisans and out of school children. My passion is not just defined by </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_0:0" style="top:1170">
<img name="_1170:827" src="page_002.jpg" height="1170" width="827" border="0" usemap="#Map"></div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1250" style="top:1250;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
the work that I have done while working with them but also, the post- completion of my initiatives </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1269" style="top:1269;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
which have prompted even my country&#146;s national government to implement the policy measures </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1289" style="top:1289;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
which were suggested out of my interventions. </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1308" style="top:1308;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
My social enterprise has registered over 10,000 direct beneficiaries and over 40,000 indirect ones in </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1327" style="top:1327;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
just over one year of operation. We have not just provided our beneficiaries with the financial </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1346" style="top:1346;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
support crutch but also empowered them to become self-sustaining individuals by ensuring </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1365" style="top:1365;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
employment for 400 men and women who gained permanent positions in our partner grassroots </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1384" style="top:1384;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
organisations and are leading an honourable life today.</span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1423" style="top:1423;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
One issue that I have been working on since past one year is to ensure quality education and bring </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1442" style="top:1442;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
down the drop-out rates of community schools in at-risk areas of India.</span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1461" style="top:1461;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
As India nears universal enrolment, there is a growing realization that bringing children into schools </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1480" style="top:1480;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
doesn&#146;t equate to quality learning. In fact, as the conversation has moved away from enrolment, </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1499" style="top:1499;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
there is an active shift towards seeking factors that deliver and influence quality. There are more </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1519" style="top:1519;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
than 400,000 community schools in India. But numerous problems like poor school infrastructure </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1538" style="top:1538;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
and learning environment, lack of adequately trained teachers, high teacher absenteeism, a large </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1557" style="top:1557;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
volume of teacher vacancies, low levels of learning and achievement and lack of accountability to </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1576" style="top:1576;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
name a few contribute to a staggering dropout rate that sees nearly 50% of children abandoning </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1595" style="top:1595;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
their education at the key transitional ages of school. Well, for me to start with, tackling all of these </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1614" style="top:1614;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
problems together would be equivalent to trying to push a wall. Hence, my motivation is towards </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1634" style="top:1634;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
solving one, &#145;the quality of content delivery and facilitation&#146;.</span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1672" style="top:1672;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
To give a sustainable solution, I founded an organisation i.e. &#145;Maslow Initiative Foundation&#146; which </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1691" style="top:1691;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
works with community schools across India. And we call the project &#145;Abrazos&#146; which means </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1710" style="top:1710;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
embracing. As the name goes, we literally adopt and embrace these schools and implement our </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1729" style="top:1729;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
innovative learning methodology.</span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1749" style="top:1749;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
Now for the implementation part, I have started working with the &#145;community schools&#146; first because </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1768" style="top:1768;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
it is the only entity with no set curriculum or teachers per say. There are more than 400,000 major </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1787" style="top:1787;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
community schools in India,  and almost one in each village/town. We are adopting such schools </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1806" style="top:1806;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
one by one and delivering our content to change lives and improve student retention rates which </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1825" style="top:1825;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
happens to be less than 10%. </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1844" style="top:1844;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
In the 10+ schools that we have already adopted, we showcase this digital content using projectors. </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1864" style="top:1864;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
Projector as a medium because, first, they are cheaper than computers or tablets (&lt;USD 12); </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1883" style="top:1883;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
second, can cater to a larger audience at once. Then comes the content transportation, which we do </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1902" style="top:1902;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
using flash drives, which is the cheapest method to do so. As of today, we have over 2000 children </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1921" style="top:1921;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
being supported by this program and that is what quenches my thirst to bring change and make a </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1940" style="top:1940;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
difference.</span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1979" style="top:1979;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
Being raised in a family where the struggle was real, I have seen the problems that I am working on </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:1998" style="top:1998;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
first hand and hence have developed that inherent passion to change what I was just forced to accept </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:2017" style="top:2017;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
in my childhood. I see the world with the perspective of providing solutions and like to call myself </span>
</div>
<div class="pos" id="_78:2036" style="top:2036;left:78">
<span id="_16.1" style=" font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:16.1px; color:#000000">
as a social enthusiast who is out there amending the dented. </span>
</div>
